race.comment: Tricky race to kick off the card with a few of these facing the starter for the first time. ENCHAANTED (9) is one of them but has shown plenty of ability at the trials and is sure to be well-educated out of the Munce yard. Draws low and should be kept very safe on debut. CERETTI (8) was thereabouts in town in both career efforts before being tipped out for time to furnish. Tuned up for this with a couple of trials and a bold showing while fresh would not surprise. BRUTAL MISS (7) is another at the races for the first time but was super impressive winning a recent Murwillumbah trial and gets a stack of weight relief with the 3kg claim. Include in calculations. HILLS OF MINTO (1) debuts off a third in a 1000m Doomben trial.
